<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-1782] Configured Environment Variables do not take effect unless also added to excludedEnvironmentVariables</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1782</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the maven environment contains a variable (ie &quot;JAVA_HOME&quot;) and it is also added to plugin configuration as below, the variable value is not seen unless configuration also contains an exclusion entry for this variable.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;environmentVariables&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;JAVA_HOME&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;junk&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/JAVA_HOME&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/environmentVariables&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;excludedEnvironmentVariables&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;excludedEnvironmentVariable&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;JAVA_HOME&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/excludedEnvironmentVariable&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/excludedEnvironmentVariables&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
